<h1>ABOUT</h1>
<p style="white-space:pre;">
    1. The Daily Journal website is a platform designed for users to maintain a personal journal or diary.
    2. The backend of the website is built using Node.js and Express.js.
    3. To ensure secure access and authentication, the website integrates Passport.js, a popular authentication middleware for Node.js.
        users can create an account, log in, and securely access their journal entries.
    4. For data storage, the website employs MongoDB, a NoSQL database, to store and manage journal entries
